{"tid":327850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰餐車撞東方航空客機　 機翼損毀","createTime":"2017-07-19T06:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T10:22:50.000Z","uid":97059,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"defa4f4bc80dca1dbff60cf2ad8c89304910bf9e","tid":327850,"uid":97059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:00:24.000Z","msg":"本港機場發生罕見「撞機」事件。昨晚一輛國泰飛機航膳餐車和一架停泊中的東方航空客機發生碰撞，導致機翼損毀。<br />\n機管局發言人指，昨晚（18日）10時左右，一輛國泰航空的飛機航膳餐車，在北衞星客運廊附近與一架中國東方航空停泊的客機碰撞，客機機翼損毀，事件中無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n有報道指，國泰餐車當時由翼底駛過，但車身高於機翼，而導致機翼摺曲。記者正就事件向國泰航空查詢，暫時未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/105915/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E9%A4%90%E8%BB%8A%E6%92%9E%E6%9D%B1%E6%96%B9%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%AE%A2%E6%A9%9F-%E6%A9%9F%E7%BF%BC%E6%90%8D%E6%AF%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F105915%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E9%25A4%2590%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%2592%259E%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25BF%25BC%25E6%2590%258D%25E6%25AF%2580&d=ntfgr0TBCPsu0edoeYNYOW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=713329e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/105915/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E9%A4%90%E8%BB%8A%E6%92%9E%E6%9D%B1%E6%96%B9%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%AE%A2%E6%A9%9F-%E6%A9%9F%E7%BF%BC%E6%90%8D%E6%AF%80</a>"},{"pid":"b613058dc312319f6d67aedc1459749ff291275d","tid":327850,"uid":24730,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:01:52.000Z","msg":"因航突襲東方"},{"pid":"51f8a489a66b09cf7950d2d817b70dde6653ada3","tid":327850,"uid":14130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:02:18.000Z","msg":"抵到爛"},{"pid":"ffcf25a2e0ade6dba9abbb0b0c68a716a6a2f54a","tid":327850,"uid":60333,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:04:04.000Z","msg":"因航：搞錯左做另一間東方，sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c383